Package com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models.student

Class Student

java.lang.Object
com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models.student.Student
@Entity public class Student extends Object
The database entity for a Student. A student is the main data point of our tool. There are a lot of things a student holds.

      private String yearInCourse
      What year the student is in the course. In the form this is a string because you can say already finished. We can not modulate it as a string because both 'already finished' and last year are possibilities. We can therefor not just convert to an int because there are many ways to state these facts.
